                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for extracting xylose from bamboo sawdust",
                    "一种竹屑提取木糖的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The embodiment of the invention provides a method for extracting xylose from bamboo sawdust. The method comprises the following steps: providing the bamboo sawdust; the method comprises the following steps: pretreating bamboo sawdust through alkaline hydrogen peroxide; carrying out acid pretreatment to obtain pretreated bamboo sawdust; hydrolyzing the pretreated bamboo sawdust to form a first hydrolysate; recovering the sugar solution and forming a second hydrolysate; neutralizing the second hydrolysate to obtain a neutralized solution; according to the technical scheme, the xylose yield efficiency is higher, meanwhile, through hydrogen peroxide pretreatment, pigments, pectin and protein are pre-removed, linkage bonds between lignin and hemicellulose are activated, the later hydrolysis effect can be improved, the yield of xylose is increased, and the yield of xylose is increased. Compared with a traditional mode, the method has the advantages that the use amount of the activated carbon is reduced by 15% or above, and the method has the advantages of being low in cost and simple in process."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明实施例提供一种竹屑提取木糖的方法，包括下述步骤：提供竹屑；通过碱性过氧化氢对竹屑进行预处理：酸预处理获取预处理竹屑：对预处理竹屑进行水解形成第一水解液；糖液回收并形成第二水解液；对第二水解液中和获取中和液；对中和液脱色、纯化、结晶得到木糖晶体等步骤获取木糖结晶，本申请的技术方案的木糖得率效率更高，同时，通过过氧化氢预处理，对色素、果胶、蛋白质起到预脱除，活化了木质素与半纤维素之间的联接键，利于后期水解效果提升，减轻了活性炭脱色负荷，对减轻木糖脱色损失、降低成本提供了基础，相比较传统方式，活性炭用量减少15％以上，具有成本低、工艺简捷特点。"
                }
            ]
        }
